    • Method Detail

      • process

        Measurement process(String projectName,
                  File projectSourceRoot,
                  File projectObjectRoot)
                    throws URISyntaxException,
                           IOException,
                           JAXBException,
                           ParserConfigurationException,
                           TransformerException,
                           ClassNotFoundException,
                           InstantiationException,
                           IllegalAccessException
        This method parses the specified folder, processing each found package, and returning a project consolidated measurement.
        Parameters:
        projectName - String the project's name.
        projectSourceRoot - File. Source root directory.
        projectObjectRoot - File. Compiled classes directory.
        Returns:
        Project consolidated measurement.
        Throws:
        URISyntaxException - in case of a resource location error.
        IOException - in case of any IO error.
        JAXBException - in case of a Marshalling / Unmarshalling error.
        ParserConfigurationException - Any DOM Parser configuration problem.
        TransformerException - In case of any problem transforming Object to XML.
        ClassNotFoundException - In case of any class load error.
        InstantiationException - In case of problems instantiating classes.
        IllegalAccessException - In case of problem trying to marshall the instances to XML.
